```{.r .cell-code}
alpha <- 0.5
beta <- 0.5
n_values <- 500

set.seed(123)
beta_values <- rbeta(n = n_values, shape1 = alpha, shape2 = beta)

plot(density(beta_values),
     main = expression(paste("Density of Beta(", alpha, " = 0.5, ", beta, " = 0.5) Distribution")),
     xlab = "Value",
     ylab = "Density",
     col = "blue",
     lwd = 2,
     cex.main = 1.2,
     cex.lab = 1.1,
     cex.axis = 1.0
)
```
